  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD SERVER</h1><p>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>The game is still in a very early Early Access version. </strong><br>We would therefore be very happy if you could share your ideas and suggestions for improvement with us so that we can optimize the game experience.<br>We have an extra channel on our Discord server for this purpose.<br><br><strong>Astronomics Rise of a new Empire</strong> is a easy to learn space real time global strategy(4X) game in which you'll create a new empire. Choose your path, whether you support the rebellion against the Eternal Empire, form a trade alliance, join the pirates or seek domination of the galaxy, only you decide.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Planet Management</h2>Control your planet, the population of your planet is divided into 3 classes with 2 subclasses each. <br>Issue directives and increase the growth of your population, but you should not neglect their satisfaction, because otherwise it can quickly come to an uprising.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/43c23395523df530668f172a29e89086.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/43c23395523df530668f172a29e89086.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/43c23395523df530668f172a29e89086.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trade Routes</h2>Build a network of trade routes between the planets to boost your faction's economy. <br>You need different materials to produce the components for your fleet in your factories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/3210c173e1c11af733d9770f82f3f28a.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/3210c173e1c11af733d9770f82f3f28a.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/3210c173e1c11af733d9770f82f3f28a.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Espionage</h2>Send spies to the planets of your enemies and allies to keep up to date with their actions. <br>If you need to sabotage a factory or eliminate a politician, it is advisable to have an experienced agent at hand.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/7ac8a9a7226840cc24129d082fe69a5e.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/7ac8a9a7226840cc24129d082fe69a5e.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/7ac8a9a7226840cc24129d082fe69a5e.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diplomacy</h2>Dive into the complex diplomacy system and conduct negotiations with other factions, make agreements, alliances or prepare your alliance for war.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/baed81f570cfa80ad238a0ac689870eb.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/baed81f570cfa80ad238a0ac689870eb.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/baed81f570cfa80ad238a0ac689870eb.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ship Design</h2>In Astronomics Rise of a new Empire you'll create your own ship designs that you can then produce in your shipyard. <br>Build your own fleet to subjugate the galaxy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/e904b80433b2b397f5acd2d2a131935a.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/e904b80433b2b397f5acd2d2a131935a.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/e904b80433b2b397f5acd2d2a131935a.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquest</h2>Destroy your enemies' fleets and conquer their planets. Astronomics Rise of a new Empire offers a complex combat system with which you'll be able to engage in battle against your enemies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/8035821205ec12c071522099b03d4f8b.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/8035821205ec12c071522099b03d4f8b.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/8035821205ec12c071522099b03d4f8b.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Politics</h2>Each of your planets has a governor and 6 ministers, these are subordinate to only one, namely your faction leader. <br>But how you fill these positions is up to you, you have different politicians at your disposal, but they all have different ambitions and goals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/585a408698f336d1a32f0bb034b42705.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/585a408698f336d1a32f0bb034b42705.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/585a408698f336d1a32f0bb034b42705.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Research</h2>Explore new technologies and discover the wonders of the galaxy.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/7a3e02ce1dfd55a525015282808c43cb.poster.avif?t=1708188391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/7a3e02ce1dfd55a525015282808c43cb.webm?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1982950/extras/7a3e02ce1dfd55a525015282808c43cb.mp4?t=1708188391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
